text: Damphreux was a municipality in Porrentruy in the canton of Jura in Switzerland. On 1 January 2024, the former municipalities of Damphreux and Lugnez merged to form the new municipality of Damphreux-Lugnez. ==References== ==Other websites== *Information in French about Damphreux on Juranet * Category:Former municipalities of Jura
